data.meta_description: New York: St. Martin's Press, 1998. First edition and first printing. Hardcover. The first book from the author of the wildly popular Da Vinci Code. A thriller set at the NSA. data.text:
New York: St. Martin's Press, 1998. First edition and first printing. Hardcover. The first book from the author of the wildly popular "Da Vinci Code." A thriller set at the NSA. A tight near fine copy with a tiny spot to the bottom edge of the pages and in a very near fine dust jacket.

Item #197220
